description: The video shows a cartoon depiction of a blonde woman with a sad expression, looking out a window. Rain streaks down the windowpane. She has fair skin, bright blue eyes, red lips, and wears a pink tank top and pearl earrings. Her blonde hair is styled in waves. She rests her face on her hand, looking mournful. To the left of her, in the window frame, is a purple vase containing a single drooping red rose, some of its petals fallen off. Green curtains hang behind her. As the video progresses, a single tear rolls down the woman's cheek. The entire scene is framed within a white window frame.
